# Screenshot Placeholders

Tambahkan screenshot berikut dari Construct 2:

## Daftar Screenshot yang Dibutuhkan:

| No | File Name | Lokasi di Construct 2 | Keterangan |
|----|-----------|----------------------|------------|
| 1 | `new-project.png` | File → New → New empty project | Dialog buat project baru |
| 2 | `layout-size.png` | Klik Layout 1 → Properties (kiri) → Layout Size | Setting ukuran layar |
| 3 | `layers-panel.png` | Panel kanan → Tab "Layers" → tombol + | Panel manage layers |
| 4 | `insert-new-object.png` | Klik kanan di Layout → Insert New Object | Menu tambah objek |
| 5 | `select-sprite.png` | Dialog "Insert New Object" → pilih Sprite | Dialog pilih tipe objek |
| 6 | `select-tilemap.png` | Dialog "Insert New Object" → pilih Tilemap | Dialog pilih Tilemap |
| 7 | `tilemap-editor.png` | Double-click Tilemap → Tilemap Editor | Editor untuk gambar level |
| 8 | `image-editor.png` | Double-click Sprite → Image Editor | Editor gambar sprite |
| 9 | `add-behavior.png` | Klik kanan Sprite → Behaviors | Menu tambah behavior |
| 10 | `select-platform-behavior.png` | Dialog "Add Behavior" → pilih Platform | Dialog pilih behavior |
| 11 | `add-global-variable.png` | Event Sheet → Klik kanan → Add global variable | Menu tambah variable |
| 12 | `instance-variable.png` | Klik Sprite → Properties → Instance variables | Variable per-objek |
| 13 | `open-event-sheet.png` | Panel Projects → Double-click Event Sheet 1 | Cara buka event sheet |
| 14 | `add-event.png` | Event Sheet → Klik kanan → Add event | Menu tambah event |

## Tips Screenshot:
- Gunakan resolusi yang jelas
- Highlight/kotak merah pada area yang penting
- Crop hanya bagian yang relevan
